description:
Watch FULL EPISODES of all of your favorite shows on The CW App! Stream your favorite CW Network shows like The Flash, Jane The Virgin, The Vampire Diaries, Arrow, Supernatural, The 100, The Originals, Beauty and the Beast, Whose Line Is It Anyway?, and America’s Next Top Model.  Then stay connected to your favorite CW Shows with the app’s push notifications. Discover CW Seed original comedies like Play It Again, Dick, The P.E.T. Squad Files, and Husbands.

Features Include:
* FULL EPISODES: Watch the latest episodes of every primetime show on The CW on demand.
* PUSH NOTIFICATIONS: Get reminders when your favorite shows air and when they're available to watch in the app.
* CLIPS: See extended videos, previews for upcoming episodes, behind-the-scenes extras, cast interviews, and more!
* PHOTOS: Browse extensive photo galleries for episodic and publicity stills.


Internet connection required. Show and episode availability subject to change. Your use is subject to Terms of Use, Mobile User Agreement and Privacy Policy. Please see links below. AppleTV/Airplay not officially supported. Use at your own risk.
releaseNotes:
* This complete redesign of the app for iOS 8 makes it easier than ever to get to the shows you want to watch
* Our video player got a suped-up, more reliable engine
* A simplified schedule page lets you know when your favorite shows air
* Streamlined photo galleries with more pictures of ridiculously attractive CW stars
* Access to exclusive CW Seed digital comedies like the "Veronica Mars" spin-off "Play It Again, Dick" and the award-winning "Husbands"
* We eradicated some bugs and left traps out for stragglers
